{"tid":373634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"俾你許三個願望 會中一個另外兩個有反效果","createTime":"2017-08-25T07:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T09:31:12.000Z","uid":46231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1180540c71a72576dc45743d5ffad3cda0844d7","tid":373634,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:03:41.000Z","msg":"如果 三個只會中一個 另外兩個會反效果 你地會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ne.g <br />\n<br />\n許願<br />\n1.變好有錢<br />\n2.變好靚仔<br />\n3.變好長命<br />\n<br />\n結果有三種<br />\n<br />\n1.變好有錢 =&gt; 實現<br />\n2.變好靚仔 =&gt; 變到好醜樣<br />\n3.變好長命 =&gt; 變到好短命<br />\n<br />\n1.變好有錢 =&gt; 變到好窮<br />\n2.變好靚仔 =&gt; 實現<br />\n3.變好長命 =&gt; 變到好短命<br />\n<br />\n1.變好有錢 =&gt; 變到好窮<br />\n2.變好靚仔 =&gt; 變到好醜樣<br />\n3.變好長命 =&gt; 實現<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以許個反面嘅願望搏佢唔中變正面<br />\n<br />\ne.g 許個願變好醜樣 如果唔中就會變好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係中左呢樣就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴絲們發揮你地創意 俾d組合黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38ec280fdd98fbb717945c466ab4696d908ce75","tid":373634,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f505e540e813e314d6f57991659d2ba99284dc","tid":373634,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2bfb85f0906086e5f443929878f7c52af2a282","tid":373634,"uid":828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:05:26.000Z","msg":"1:女神做左我女朋友<br />\n2:我做左女神男朋友<br />\n3:我同女神拍拖<br />\n<br />\n秒"},{"pid":"361e0b3612fbb72b8b295e5ebd52457825ab96e9","tid":373634,"uid":94090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit